theme_override_styles/normal = SubResource("StyleBoxEmpty_gpa2e")
text = "\"One day, on my way back from school, I saw a cyclist pass by, with a massive camera hanging from their neck.
                                                                   
My eyes lingered on them  for a little while, for no particular reason, and I noticed them abruptly stop, point their lens off to the side, take a photo, and continue on their path.
                                                                   
' I wonder what made them take that photo? '
So I diverged off my usual trail, entranced by the curiosity, to see for myself what could've possibly been so captivating.
                                                                 
I wasn't disappointed. It was beautiful.
It was one of those scenes that seem out of a movie. A white scooter surrounded by pink leaves. The sun at the perfect angle, creating a fabulous sheen on the clean body of the Vespa.
                                                                             
I wonder what would've happened if I didn't notice the cyclist, or if I didn't let myself get carried by the current of coincidences. Maybe I don't want to know.
I'll never forget this memory, it defines who I am.\"
                                                        
[Press X to forget]"
